00:21:59.518 --> 00:22:01.284
hot Zhibov gezogt, neyn yidn.

00:22:02.539 --> 00:22:06.954
bin ikh avekgegangen mit, hot men aroysgevorfn Zhibovn, ven er hot gehat dem letstn briv fun zey.

00:22:08.192 --> 00:22:10.970
zog ikh, dos vet nit forkum- zogt Zhibov zogt, dos vet nit forkumen.

00:22:11.052 --> 00:22:15.322
zogt er, Khatskel, zogt er, du vilst tsuleygn, zogt er, mit Kalmen, zog ikh, ya, ikh mit Kalmen leygn mir zikh

00:22:15.322 --> 00:22:18.362
tsu un di iberike vos aroysgevorfene ho'mir ale tsugeleygt.

00:22:19.684 --> 00:22:22.040
ho'mir zikh antzagt optsugebn zey di shul.

00:22:22.367 --> 00:22:24.740
hobn zey undz gefodert az mir zoln makhn

00:22:24.797 --> 00:22:26.799
nit ineveynik, nor fun oysveynik,

00:22:27.278 --> 00:22:29.938
zi zol oyszen vi zi darf tsu zayn.

00:22:30.788 --> 00:22:33.127
zey veysn dokh keyn iz nit gelt, di yidn zaynen nito,

00:22:35.023 --> 00:22:37.632
un in der tsayt hob ikh gekrogn a mashin

00:22:39.917 --> 00:22:43.474
nu m'hot gegebn in di in di arbets-teyl hot gegebn mashines

00:22:43.474 --> 00:22:44.872
far di gute arbeter.

00:22:46.650 --> 00:22:48.568
hob ikh gedarft ibertsoln far der mashin.

00:22:49.570 --> 00:22:54.036
hob ikh mit mayn bruder adurkhgeforn

00:22:55.560 --> 00:22:57.478
in halb Lite un zukhndik di gelt.

00:22:57.687 --> 00:22:58.848
undz kenen der-

00:22:58.848 --> 00:23:01.899
dos kenen ⟨dertseyln⟩ Telzer yidn, Vorner yidn,

00:23:02.091 --> 00:23:04.144
Lupliker yidn, Uzvilter yidn,

00:23:04.437 --> 00:23:07.698
Krozer yidn, Reseyner yidn,

00:23:07.698 --> 00:23:10.050
Shkudviler yidn, Shavler yidn,

00:23:10.377 --> 00:23:12.615
un mir hobn gemakht, tsamgeklibn gelt

00:23:13.161 --> 00:23:15.737
un di yidn ale hobn afile nit gefregt

00:23:16.249 --> 00:23:20.681
mayne mayn pas mit ale, nor ikh hob aleyn zey forgeshtelt, ot iz mayn pas,

00:23:21.058 --> 00:23:29.709
ot iz der nomen fun der mashin un mir zaynen gekumen do far zikh epes nemen gelt. mir hobn nor gefregt eyn zakh, "in Kovne darf men likvidrn di shul oder men darf ir ophaltn?" ale yidn,

00:23:30.171 --> 00:23:33.810
afile in Vorne, hot gelebt a froy mit a litviner,

00:23:34.592 --> 00:23:37.630
a lererke iz zi nokh dem geven, hot zi oykh gezogt, zogt zi,

00:23:37.765 --> 00:23:42.365
neyn, zogt zi, khaveyrim, zogt zi, yede shul, zogt er, darf men bahitn!

00:23:42.523 --> 00:23:45.149
zog ikh, damolts leygt zikh tsu tsum gebn gelt. ale mol.

00:23:46.337 --> 00:23:51.202
un mir hobn gegebn dem heysn vort

00:23:51.202 --> 00:23:54.634
mit vos mir kenen zey bavayzn az mir op- az mir makhn di shul,

00:23:54.690 --> 00:23:57.266
ho'mir opgefotografirt in groysn

00:23:58.133 --> 00:24:01.333
PIZO- in a in aza minen formatn,

00:23:59.753 --> 00:24:00.709
format.

00:24:01.626 --> 00:24:05.973
un nokh dem un farshribn alemen vu eyner hot gelebt in Lite un mir hobn ale oys geshikt

00:24:06.132 --> 00:24:08.792
dem bild fun di shul, iz geven opgeshtelt.

00:24:09.034 --> 00:24:10.192
dos iz geven fun oysnveynik.

00:24:11.734 --> 00:24:13.736
hobn zey shoyn nit gekent mer tsu ⟨tsunemen⟩ fun undz.

00:24:14.113 --> 00:24:17.347
un azoy hot ir hot ir opgeratevet di shul.

00:24:16.617 --> 00:24:17.487
di shul.

00:24:17.792 --> 00:24:20.351
un haynt tsu tog arbet ir in di zelbiker shul?

00:24:20.205 --> 00:24:21.026
ya.

00:24:20.813 --> 00:24:22.494
ver zayt ir in shul?

00:24:22.062 --> 00:24:25.127
ikh bin der gabe fun shul, m'hot mir oysgeklibn der gabe fun shul.

00:24:25.285 --> 00:24:26.156
az,

00:24:25.318 --> 00:24:28.350
mir hobn, mir'n mir danken di amerikaner yidn,

00:24:28.440 --> 00:24:31.302
un mir danken di yidn fun gants velt vos hobn undz geholfn.

00:24:31.866 --> 00:24:34.647
mir hobn gemakht di shul, vi azoy ikh farshtey,

00:24:34.647 --> 00:24:35.997
az ikh hob gef- gehert

00:24:35.997 --> 00:24:38.435
di yidn fun Amerike vos zaynen geven tsu gast.

00:24:38.435 --> 00:24:42.949
un andere yidn fun Erets- un az s'kumen tsu forn fun gants velt di yidn haynt in Kovner shul,

00:24:42.949 --> 00:24:44.890
zogn az Kovner hokh-shul

00:24:44.890 --> 00:24:47.674
iz eyne fun di shenster in der velt mit zayn orn-koydesh,

00:24:47.674 --> 00:24:52.717
halt ikh az ikh hob geton a groyser zakh mit mayne mithelfer,

00:24:53.280 --> 00:24:56.129
ongefirt ineveynik tsu makhn dem gantsn

00:24:56.129 --> 00:24:58.877
remont in di shul, hob ikh on a inzhenir

00:24:59.203 --> 00:25:03.309
on a keynen andere groyse mithelfer,

00:25:03.309 --> 00:25:05.593
ikh bin nit keyn hoykh-gelernter mentsh,

00:25:05.650 --> 00:25:07.174
ikh bin a arbeter-mentsh,

00:25:07.174 --> 00:25:08.833
nor ikh hob a yidisher harts.

00:25:08.873 --> 00:25:11.088
nor vifl mir kenen tuen mir.

00:25:11.088 --> 00:25:14.666
haynt tsum tog, zog ikh, iz do a got oyf der velt.

00:25:14.666 --> 00:25:16.123
mir zaynen gekumen in shul

00:25:16.483 --> 00:25:19.548
mentshn, mir hobn ale tog fertsik, fuftsik mentshn.

00:25:19.791 --> 00:25:25.877
vayle ts- di gevezene groyse ofitsirn in Sovyetn Farband, UNK polkovnikes mit UNK,

00:25:26.136 --> 00:25:30.267
un oykh andere yidn vos hobn geven, zaynen geven parteyner in di Sovyetn-Farband,

00:25:30.267 --> 00:25:31.246
hobn zikh ge-

00:25:31.246 --> 00:25:34.753
s'kumen haynt in shul un mir freyt dos,

00:25:34.860 --> 00:25:40.291
mir freyt zeyer az mir hobn gekent tsutsien dem ⟨yingtum⟩ brengen vider tsu yidishkeyt.

00:25:40.291 --> 00:25:44.164
mir makhn haynt khupes, mir makhn bal-mitsves, mir makhn

00:25:44.164 --> 00:25:46.954
mir makhn m'baerdikt mentshn m'zogt nokh yidishn din.

00:25:47.112 --> 00:25:53.721
ikh bin zeyer tsufridn vos vos got hot undz gehelfn, gegebn mir gezunt tsum helfn

00:25:53.794 --> 00:25:57.112
do di shul opshteln, un az m'geyt in shul,

00:25:57.152 --> 00:25:58.968
un s'vet zikh nokh veln merer

00:25:59.093 --> 00:26:00.825
az m'zol undz helfn tsu di shul.

00:26:01.438 --> 00:26:04.554
a groysn dank aykh, s'kumt aykh a groyser yasher-koyekh

00:26:04.797 --> 00:26:07.662
far dem vos ir hot geratevet dem di Kovner shul,

00:26:07.662 --> 00:26:11.422
vos ir halt ir oyset, un ikh gib aykh a groysn a hartsikn dank

00:26:11.428 --> 00:26:13.312
far aza sheynem intervyu.

00:26:13.757 --> 00:26:14.983
danken sheyn aykh.

