00:26:31.206 --> 00:26:34.830
dos iz a vayb's Shokyaner besoylem amolikn.

00:26:34.830 --> 00:26:35.806
dos iz befor di krig.

00:26:36.522 --> 00:26:40.987
eyner Meshe Moyshe Izak gefint zikh itster in Erets-Yisroel.

00:26:40.673 --> 00:26:42.995
in viflte yor iz gemakht gevorn der bild do?

00:26:42.445 --> 00:26:44.093
