redt redt bite!

00:26:54.600 --> 00:26:56.006
dertseylt vos iz dos?

00:26:55.506 --> 00:26:56.985
dos iz der bild

00:26:57.008 --> 00:27:00.934
iz geboyrn gevorn in akht un draysikstn yor, nit lang far di krig,

00:27:00.990 --> 00:27:05.084
ikh bin dort oyfn rekht der tsveyter mit a hitl derfar vayl ikh hob nit gehat keyn yarmlke.

00:27:05.142 --> 00:27:06.553
u- un,

00:27:05.175 --> 00:27:11.340
UNK dos. ale maynershe kleyner kinder, mayne kha- mayne shvesterkinder, mayne bakante UNK, mayne lerers,

