mayne tsvey rabonim, Shokyaner,

00:27:13.444 --> 00:27:17.690
un a lererke, dos ale ale zaynen derharget gevorn, ale zaynen gevorn derfarmordert.

00:27:17.410 --> 00:27:19.884
un vos iz dos oyfn bild do? der kheyder fun Shukyan?

00:27:19.350 --> 00:27:20.778
der kheyder fun Shukyan.

