un z- oyf yidish zogt es nokh a mol.

00:27:36.124 --> 00:27:44.474
do der bild iz gemakht gevorn long for der krig, mayn bruder Zalmen hot gedint in di in di litvishe armey, er shteyt der

00:27:44.474 --> 00:27:45.967
in dem bild in der rekht-

00:27:45.967 --> 00:27:47.474
der ershter fun rekhts,

00:27:47.616 --> 00:27:49.098
fun links mistame?

00:27:48.274 --> 00:27:49.415
fun links.

00:27:50.147 --> 00:27:52.768
un er iz ge- im hot men dershosn

00:27:52.768 --> 00:27:54.900
in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

