der bild shteyt do in di Shukyaner, UNK fun Shukyan,

00:28:11.494 --> 00:28:15.386
vos iz oysgeshosn al- di ale Shuk- Shukyaner yidn,

00:28:15.561 --> 00:28:17.580
shtey ikh do fun rekht der ershter,

00:28:17.856 --> 00:28:21.025
shteyt do mayn bruder fun link der ersht- der ershter,

00:28:21.025 --> 00:28:23.869
mayn shvesterkind in Yizrael, Meyer Melts,

00:28:23.869 --> 00:28:25.899
a Linkover yid, Tseyl Girts.

