dos iz mayn froy Nelin,

00:28:31.457 --> 00:28:36.075
vos zi halt mir unter in undzer getrayen lebn.

00:28:36.267 --> 00:28:40.631
nit lang bin ikh geven in Erets- in in tsu gast in Amerike in Los-Andzheles,

00:28:41.076 --> 00:28:43.781
hob zikh getrofn mit a sakh rabonim,

00:28:43.781 --> 00:28:45.406
mit a, un geven in a sakh shuln,

00:28:45.632 --> 00:28:47.836
un ikh bin zeyer dankbar

